## Image Credits

All NASA imagery used on this site is in the public domain per NASA media usage guidelines:
https://www.nasa.gov/nasa-brand-center/images-and-media/

Specific images:
- KSC-20221116-PH-CLC03_0002 — Artemis I Liftoff (NASA / Kennedy Space Center)
- art002e016299 — Earthrise Captured by Orion / Artemis I (NASA)
- 1300435 — Marshall Space Flight Center Building 4200 (NASA / MSFC)
- jsc2023e018469 — Artemis II Crew (NASA)

SpaceX imagery (where used) is provided under SpaceX's open license policy.
See: https://www.spacex.com/

Code in this repository is MIT licensed.
Images retain their original NASA public domain / SpaceX open license terms.
